[SN]TITLE[SN]
Morgan Escare: Wigan Warriors and France back signs contract extension

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Wigan Warriors full-back Morgan Escare has agreed a new contract to stay with the Super League side until 2020.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 24-year-old France international joined Warriors from Catalans on a one-year deal at the start of the season and has impressed in his 10 games.
"I am really happy here at Wigan and feel at home," he said.
"I'm enjoying my rugby too and am happy with the way I am playing. It's great to have this new contract agreed and I am excited for the future."
His new contract also includes a one-year option to extend the deal at the end of 2020.
